WEBVTT

00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:02.040
Why do I know it by heart?

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:04.400
Because he said it to me.

00:07:05.640 --> 00:07:07.136
Crazy.

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:09.840
And I said, "Hallelujah."

00:07:10.800 --> 00:07:13.296
But more than that, I said,

00:07:13.320 --> 00:07:15.016
"What an opportunity."

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:16.536
You know what I was thinking?

00:07:16.560 --> 00:07:19.016
It was at an event
that we were doing on the subject

00:07:19.040 --> 00:07:20.976
at Georgetown University in May of 2015.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:23.776
And I thought, this is the solution

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:27.296
to the biggest problem
facing America today. What?

00:07:27.320 --> 00:07:30.096
It's coming together around these ideas,